          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1693819772687-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reheat the<strong> enchilada topping</strong> over a high heat for 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened to a double cream consistency</p><p>Meanwhile, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Trim and slice your<strong> spring onion[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>finely</p><p>Grease an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> (or two!) with a little<strong> vegetable oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1693819775497-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1693819775497-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
